message.body: Thanks again so much for last night!! I couldn't have pulled that off without you :) :)
Tell Hunter thank you too!
Julian loved his chicken bowl...this morning he said, I think that chicken bowl was a really special gift from Hunter.
Lol!! Ahahahaha! Hunter was really happy to give it to him! I had a blast!
I have your chairs and chips for you!
Did you get to have any pie?? I can bring you some if you want me to!
Julian is such a pie hog!
I ate pie!! It was so good!
I want to make another one. I'm going to bed bath and beyond do you need to go to New Jersey for anything?

ew jersey, but gotta go to work soon!
